{"tid":1855712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★研究指雙黃連可抑制新型冠狀病毒後　多個平台售罄","createTime":"2020-02-01T08:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T04:22:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"17306ad4c6965cac83a0b358171356fec16cfd3c","tid":1855712,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"中國科學院上海藥物所及武漢病毒所聯合研究初步發現，中成藥「雙黃連口服液」可抑制新型冠狀病毒。消息傳出後，多個網上平台的「雙黃連口服液」，都已經售罄或下架。<br />\n<br />\n「雙黃連口服液」由金銀花、黃芩及連翹三款中藥組成，中醫認為，這三款中藥具有清熱解毒、表裡雙清的作用。現代醫學研究認為，「雙黃連口服液」具有抗病毒、抑菌、提高免疫功能的作用，是目前有效的抗病毒藥物之一。<br />\n<br />\n上海藥物所長期從事抗病毒藥物研究，2003年沙士期間，曾率先證實「雙黃連口服液」具有抗沙士病毒的作用，十多年來亦陸續證實「雙黃連口服液」對流感病毒、沙士及中東呼吸綜合症病毒，具有明顯的抗病毒效應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505980-20200201.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505980-20200201.htm&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ii3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=afcdbb59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505980-20200201.htm&h=360a95dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505980-20200201.htm</a>"},{"pid":"49320ded98322da1c4dd6cda875e18d7026ec3ba","tid":1855712,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08141e47c57fb15c099cfd85afd89c534436bb1","tid":1855712,"uid":226955,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"遲啲五糧液都可以醫百病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"